BAIXE AQUI SUA IMAGEM EM ALTA QUALIDADE
Preview prompt
widgets_values:
Got it, I need to describe the image in detail to preserve exactly the same thing. Let's start by looking at the main elements.

First, the subject is a person with a dark background. The person has short, dark hair styled upwards. The face is split into two colors: left side (from the viewer's perspective) is orange, right side is green. The orange is on the left cheek and part of the jawline, while the green covers the right cheek, nose, and part of the jaw. The skin texture on the colored areas looks like a textured paste or mask, not smooth. The person has a mustache and some stubble on the chin. The eyes are brown, looking directly at the camera. The background is solid black, which makes the colors stand out. The person is wearing a black top, visible at the neck. Let's check each detail: hair color (dark brown/black), style (updo), face split (left orange, right green), texture of the colors (textured, not smooth), facial hair (mustache, stubble), eye color (brown), background (black), clothing (black top). Need to make sure all these elements are included without adding or omitting anything.
</think>
